OL,4,CLow-deposit mortgage scheme is launched
OL,5, High Street lenders are now starting to
OL,6, offer mortgages to borrowers offering a
OL,7, deposit of just 5% under a new
OL,8, government guarantee scheme.
OL,10,FThe policy, announced in the Budget, is
OL,11,Fdesigned to help more first-time buyers
OL,12,Fsecure a home.
OL,14,FBut the launch comes as average house
OL,15,Fprices in the UK continue to rise to
OL,16,Frecord levels.
OL,18,FAnalysts also suggest that cheaper
OL,19,Fdeals are available for those able to
OL,20,Fstretch to a 10% deposit.
